{"id":"b5e4c2fb-461d-4719-ab01-931d8598677d","name":"⚠️You startled the Witch","description":"<h1 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>\"I'll give her a reason to cry about\"</strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p>You're a lone survivor in the middle of the Green Flu apocalypse, and while seeking refuge you entered a building that looked safe. That's when you notice it, the loud crying of a nearby Witch. You should just mind your business and let her be, to make sure you leave that place in one piece.</p><p>Or you can try taming her with your meat.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://imgchest.com/p/wl7l9683q7x\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>CLICK HERE TO SEE EXTRA PICS</strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://rule34.xxx/index.php?page=post&amp;s=view&amp;id=9578721\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 508px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" alt=\"witch\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/3h3inf.gif\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">Perfect time to make a Left 4 Dead 2 bot, since it's trending thanks to the Halloween sales. I still don't know why I'm able to keep making bots with the funny pumpkin icon since Halloween is gone, but hey I'm not against it.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">[2D art generated by me, using Androjuniarto's style.]<br>[To get the source of the 3D art just click on the images]</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 461px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/d289f5e8-5a50-477e-8bdc-b41688d1b000_d01a15e9-43c3-4ade-a074-ca09f9bfff40.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 688px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile